TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
select distinct i.ITEM_ID, i.ATTRIBUTION_CODE, s.COMPANY_CODE, s.DIVISION_CODE as DIVISION_CODE, i.DIVISION_GROUP as division_group, i.STYLE_NUM, s.REPRESENTATIVE_STYLE_NUM, i.COLOR_CODE, i.SIZE_CODE, i.CUP_SIZE, i.X_SIZE, i.SIZE_POS, i.SIZE_LINE, i.PACK_CODE, s.STYLE_GROUP, s.BUSINESS_SEG_DESC, s.SBU_DESC, i.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, s.BRAND_NAME, s.CAPACITY_GROUP, s.SUBBRAND_DESC, s.COLOR_CATEGORY_DESC, s.BRAND_GROUP_DESC, s.BRAND_OWNERSHIP_GROUP_DESC, s.LEVEL_1_NAME, s.GENDER_DESC, s.GENDER_CATEGORY_DESC, s.MARKETING_LOB_GROUP, s.PRODUCT_GROUP_DESC, s.CATEGORY_DESC, s.SUBCATEGORY_DESC, s.SILHOUETTE, max(i.UPDATE_TIMESTAMP), i.DISCONTINUED_DATE , s.PRODUCT_LINE_DESC as PRODUCT_LINE_DESC, i.SAP_WHOLESALE_PRICE , i.SAP_GRID_VALUE as SAP_GRID_VALUE, i.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM from hsf_item i, slba_item si, style_master_1 s, hsf_SKU_LIFECYCLE_CLASS_L slc where
i.item_id = si.item_id and
i.style_num=s.style_num and i.item_id=SLC.item_id and SLC.start_date >=ADD_MONTHS(sysdate,-36) and SLC.MAPPED_CLASS_CODE=1 and i.UPDATE_USERID not like '%HSF%' and trim(i.item_type_code) = 'SEL' and i.division_group=s.division_group and s.SBU_DESC in (select distinct SBU_DESC from FCST_FINANCE_CONTROL) and trim (upper (s.style_group)) != 'UNMAPPED'
and i.division_group='mex'
group by i.ITEM_ID, i.ATTRIBUTION_CODE, s.COMPANY_CODE, s.DIVISION_CODE, i.DIVISION_GROUP, i.STYLE_NUM, s.REPRESENTATIVE_STYLE_NUM, i.COLOR_CODE, i.SIZE_CODE, i.CUP_SIZE, i.X_SIZE, i.SIZE_POS, i.SIZE_LINE, i.PACK_CODE, s.STYLE_GROUP, s.BUSINESS_SEG_DESC, s.SBU_DESC, i.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, s.BRAND_NAME, s.CAPACITY_GROUP, s.SUBBRAND_DESC, s.COLOR_CATEGORY_DESC, s.BRAND_GROUP_DESC, s.BRAND_OWNERSHIP_GROUP_DESC, s.LEVEL_1_NAME, s.GENDER_DESC, s.GENDER_CATEGORY_DESC, s.MARKETING_LOB_GROUP, s.PRODUCT_GROUP_DESC, s.CATEGORY_DESC, s.SUBCATEGORY_DESC, s.SILHOUETTE, i.DISCONTINUED_DATE, s.PRODUCT_LINE_DESC, i.SAP_WHOLESALE_PRICE, i.SAP_GRID_VALUE, i.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM union select distinct i.ITEM_ID, i.ATTRIBUTION_CODE, s.COMPANY_CODE, s.DIVISION_CODE as DIVISION_CODE, i.DIVISION_GROUP as division_group, i.STYLE_NUM, s.REPRESENTATIVE_STYLE_NUM, i.COLOR_CODE, i.SIZE_CODE, i.CUP_SIZE, i.X_SIZE, i.SIZE_POS, i.SIZE_LINE, i.PACK_CODE, s.STYLE_GROUP, s.BUSINESS_SEG_DESC, s.SBU_DESC, i.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY , s.BRAND_NAME, s.CAPACITY_GROUP, s.SUBBRAND_DESC, s.COLOR_CATEGORY_DESC, s.BRAND_GROUP_DESC, s.BRAND_OWNERSHIP_GROUP_DESC, s.LEVEL_1_NAME, s.GENDER_DESC, s.GENDER_CATEGORY_DESC, s.MARKETING_LOB_GROUP, s.PRODUCT_GROUP_DESC, s.CATEGORY_DESC, s.SUBCATEGORY_DESC, s.SILHOUETTE, max(i.UPDATE_TIMESTAMP), i.DISCONTINUED_DATE, s.PRODUCT_LINE_DESC as PRODUCT_LINE_DESC, i.SAP_WHOLESALE_PRICE, i.SAP_GRID_VALUE as SAP_GRID_VALUE, i.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM from hsf_item i,slba_item si, style_master_1 s where
i.item_id = si.item_id and
i.style_num=s.style_num
and i.UPDATE_USERID like '%HSF%'
and trim(i.item_type_code) = 'SEL' and i.division_group=s.division_group and s.SBU_DESC in (select distinct SBU_DESC from FCST_FINANCE_CONTROL) and trim (upper (s.style_group)) != 'UNMAPPED'
and i.division_group='mex'
group by i.ITEM_ID, i.ATTRIBUTION_CODE, s.COMPANY_CODE, s.DIVISION_CODE, i.DIVISION_GROUP, i.STYLE_NUM, s.REPRESENTATIVE_STYLE_NUM, i.COLOR_CODE, i.SIZE_CODE, i.CUP_SIZE, i.X_SIZE, i.SIZE_POS, i.SIZE_LINE, i.PACK_CODE, s.STYLE_GROUP, s.BUSINESS_SEG_DESC, s.SBU_DESC, i.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, s.BRAND_NAME, s.CAPACITY_GROUP, s.SUBBRAND_DESC, s.COLOR_CATEGORY_DESC, s.BRAND_GROUP_DESC, s.BRAND_OWNERSHIP_GROUP_DESC, s.LEVEL_1_NAME, s.GENDER_DESC, s.GENDER_CATEGORY_DESC, s.MARKETING_LOB_GROUP, s.PRODUCT_GROUP_DESC, s.CATEGORY_DESC, s.SUBCATEGORY_DESC, s.SILHOUETTE, i.DISCONTINUED_DATE, s.PRODUCT_LINE_DESC, i.SAP_WHOLESALE_PRICE, i.SAP_GRID_VALUE, i.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM union select distinct i.ITEM_ID, i.ATTRIBUTION_CODE, s.COMPANY_CODE, s.DIVISION_CODE as DIVISION_CODE, i.DIVISION_GROUP as division_group, i.STYLE_NUM , s.REPRESENTATIVE_STYLE_NUM, i.COLOR_CODE , i.SIZE_CODE , i.CUP_SIZE , i.X_SIZE, i.SIZE_POS, i.SIZE_LINE, i.PACK_CODE, s.STYLE_GROUP, s.BUSINESS_SEG_DESC, s.SBU_DESC, i.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, s.BRAND_NAME, s.CAPACITY_GROUP, s.SUBBRAND_DESC, s.COLOR_CATEGORY_DESC, s.BRAND_GROUP_DESC, s.BRAND_OWNERSHIP_GROUP_DESC, s.LEVEL_1_NAME, s.GENDER_DESC, s.GENDER_CATEGORY_DESC, s.MARKETING_LOB_GROUP, s.PRODUCT_GROUP_DESC, s.CATEGORY_DESC, s.SUBCATEGORY_DESC, s.SILHOUETTE, max(i.UPDATE_TIMESTAMP), i.DISCONTINUED_DATE , s.PRODUCT_LINE_DESC as PRODUCT_LINE_DESC, i.SAP_WHOLESALE_PRICE, i.SAP_GRID_VALUE as SAP_GRID_VALUE, i.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM from hsf_item i,slba_item si, style_master_1 s where
i.item_id = si.item_id and
i.style_num=s.style_num and i.item_id NOT IN (select SLC.item_id from hsf_SKU_LIFECYCLE_CLASS_L slc where SLC.start_date >=ADD_MONTHS(sysdate,-36) and SLC.MAPPED_CLASS_CODE=1 ) and i.UPDATE_USERID not like '%HSF%' and trim(i.item_type_code) = 'SEL' and i.division_group=s.division_group and s.SBU_DESC in (select distinct SBU_DESC from FCST_FINANCE_CONTROL) and trim (upper (s.style_group)) != 'UNMAPPED'
and i.division_group ='mex'
group by i.ITEM_ID, i.ATTRIBUTION_CODE, s.COMPANY_CODE, s.DIVISION_CODE, i.DIVISION_GROUP, i.STYLE_NUM , s.REPRESENTATIVE_STYLE_NUM, i.COLOR_CODE, i.SIZE_CODE, i.CUP_SIZE, i.X_SIZE, i.SIZE_POS, i.SIZE_LINE, i.PACK_CODE, s.STYLE_GROUP, s.BUSINESS_SEG_DESC, s.SBU_DESC, i.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, s.BRAND_NAME, s.CAPACITY_GROUP, s.SUBBRAND_DESC, s.COLOR_CATEGORY_DESC, s.BRAND_GROUP_DESC, s.BRAND_OWNERSHIP_GROUP_DESC, s.LEVEL_1_NAME, s.GENDER_DESC, s.GENDER_CATEGORY_DESC, s.MARKETING_LOB_GROUP, s.PRODUCT_GROUP_DESC, s.CATEGORY_DESC, s.SUBCATEGORY_DESC, s.SILHOUETTE, i.DISCONTINUED_DATE, s.PRODUCT_LINE_DESC, i.SAP_WHOLESALE_PRICE, i.SAP_GRID_VALUE, i.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM
